<L>__{interior house entry hall night}
<A>__{the doorbell chimes. the hostess, connie, a pleasant looking woman, answers the door.}
<C>__{barnes}
<D>__{hi! bob barnes! looks like a swell party!}
<C>__{connie}
<P>__{(pleased)}
<D>__{frances!}
<A>__{as they embrace, frances looks around with trepidation:}
<C>__{frances}
<P>__{(whisper)}
<D>__{god, who's here?}
<C>__{connie}
<P>__{(also whispering)}
<D>__{the usual vermin, i'm afraid.}
<A>__{barnes tries to pull frances inside. she sees a flurry of waiting faces. everyone's watching her.}
<C>__{frances}
<P>__{(sotto voice)}
<D>__{get me a drink.}
<A>__{barnes nods, concerned, and crosses to the bar.}
<C>__{frances}
<D>__{hi everybody.}
<A>__{some people seem amused, some curious, some scornful. the director from the mud scene nods to her. connie is at her side for support. a voice from somewhere pierces the chatter:}
<C>__{snide voice}
<D>__{so nice to have you back, frances.}
<A>__{as barnes returns with her drink, she turns to connie:}
<C>__{frances}
<D>__{connie, can i use the upstairs bathroom?}
<C>__{connie}
<D>__{sure.}
